+# 🔐 Inferno Security Policy
+
+## Supported Versions
+| Version | Supported  |
+|:---------|:------------|
+| Main     | ✅   |
+| Dev Branches | ⚠️ Security review required |
+
+## Reporting a Vulnerability
+If you discover a security issue, please follow these steps:
+
+1. **Do not create a public issue.**  
+2. Send a confidential email to 📧 security@inferno.dev  
+3. Include a clear description of the problem, its impact and proof-of-concept (if possible).  
+4. You will receive a response within 48 hours and a resolution plan within 7 days.  
+
+All valid vulnerability reports will be acknowledged and credited in future security updates.  
+
+## Security Audits & Bug Bounty
+Audits will be conducted for core contracts (Token, BuybackVault, Presale, Vesting) by independent firms.  
+A community bug bounty program will be launched after mainnet deployment.  
